message.body: I take back what I said about the talking heads
Hey! That's wonderful. How did that happen?
Exposure and being a little more open. How are you?
I'm well. Feeling good and healthy. Bored at home. But I should be hired by the end of the week hopefully. Anxious to get back to minnesota ultimately.
What are you getting hired as?
Either a librarian or doing data entry for a group that does case management for foster boys.

It's great. Totally challenging, immersive, and inspiring. I'm really growing as an artist, but definitely feel stripped of anything I held true precious to this which is dizzying - but important. Work sounds promising! Those positions sound great.
Just temporary jobs. Hoping to save a bit so I can move back up to mn in 3 or so months.
Nice, the sometimes snowy state misses you :) and I'm glad you're healthy.
I'm glad to hear the place is working out so well for you.
